#: ../../H/hacked-up.rst:5
msgid "hacked up"
msgstr "hacked up"

#: ../../H/hacked-up.rst:7
msgid "adj\\."
msgstr "形容詞"

#: ../../H/hacked-up.rst:9
msgid ""
"Sufficiently patched, kluged, and tweaked that the surgical scars are "
"beginning to crowd out normal tissue (compare :ref:`critical-mass`\\). Not "
"all programs that are hacked become hacked up; if modifications are done "
"with some eye to coherence and continued maintainability, the software may "
"emerge better for the experience. Contrast :ref:`hack-up`\\."
msgstr ""
"外科手術の傷跡が正常な組織を押しのけ始めるほど十分にパッチを当てられ、kludgeされ、いじられた状態(\\ :ref:`critical-"
"mass`\\ と比較せよ)。ハックされたプログラムがすべてhacked "
"upになるわけではない。整合性と継続的な保守性に多少気を配って変更がなされれば、ソフトウェアはその経験によってかえって良くなるかもしれない。\\ "
":ref:`hack-up`\\ と対照せよ。"
